org.netbeans.api.io

Class OutputWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.Writer
      • java.io.PrintWriter
        • org.netbeans.api.io.OutputWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, Flushable, Appendable, AutoCloseable

    public abstract class OutputWriter
extends PrintWriter
    Extended PrintWriter for writing into output window or similar output GUI component. It can support features like color printing, hyperlinks, or folding.

    Methods of this class can be called in any thread.
